Canny Defense			KEY:Kensai ~ Canny Defense				CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:MagusClassFeatures.Extraordinary.ArchetypeAbility.SpecialQuality			DEFINE:CannyDefenseLVL|0	DEFINE:TotalACBonus|0	DEFINE:ActualACBonus|0	DESC:At 1st level, when a kensai is wielding his chosen weapon, he gains the canny defense ability. This is identical to the duelist prestige class ability of the same name (Core Rulebook 382), save that his chosen weapon may be of any type. [AC Bonus +%1 / Actual AC Bonus +%2]|TotalACBonus|ActualACBonus																																																																																																																																																																																																																																	BONUS:COMBAT|AC|max(0,min(INT,CannyDefenseLVL))|TYPE=Dodge|PREMULT:2,[!PREEQUIP:1,ARMORTYPE=Medium,ARMORTYPE=Heavy,TYPE=Shield],[PREEQUIP:1,TYPE=Melee,TYPE=Ranged]	BONUS:VAR|TotalACBonus|max(0,min(INT,CannyDefenseLVL))	BONUS:VAR|ActualACBonus|max(0,min(INT,CannyDefenseLVL))|TYPE=Dodge|PREMULT:2,[!PREEQUIP:1,ARMORTYPE=Medium,ARMORTYPE=Heavy,TYPE=Shield],[PREEQUIP:1,TYPE=Melee,TYPE=Ranged]	BONUS:VAR|CannyDefenseLVL|MagusLVL						SOURCEPAGE:p.55
